    YONG HAIWEN FED PROJECT
    Design process
    This website focus was mainly on people who want to buy a pc in a very easy manner, aas well as rovide a cheap experience for them to take in. I started by reusing an old website that I had made on wix and converted it into my website which was firestorm pc. Starting with the color scheme of orange and blue I felt it was a quite fitting design.

    Features
    Feature 1:Allows users to browse through the different computers on offer
    Feature 2: Allows users to view the awards and about of how my pc cpmpany was founded
    Feature 3: Give us a back to top feature once at the bottom
    Feature 4: Lets users convert to phone media to use this website

    Technologies used

    Boxicons
    I have used https://boxicons.com/?query=box boxicons which is an website which allows me to import icons easily. This allows me to not use images and use many other different icons to represent different things such as the back to top button icon and features of firestorm pc

    Javascript
    I used javascript to implement the feature of the the back to top button

    HTML
    I used html to put in the basics such as what is going to happen as well as all of the contents of the website such as the images, the text or icons in the site.

    CSS
    I used CSS in order to style the content that is inside of the website, for example, I used CSS to move the icons and boxes of the website where I need it to be. I also used CSS to change the font style as well as the font color so that my HTML will be neater when I am working on the HTML programme.

    Testing
    While testing, I found that my icons kept on changing the very minute I had move the page. I later found out this was because I had not alocated the @media query. Thus, i made sure that  when my website had rezsized to different sizes for example phone size and different monitor sizes, I always make sure that the screen size does not affect what is on my website. For example for the description on why you should use firestorm pc instead of other brands, I had changed it 1x4, so 4 descriptions in 1 line to a 2x2 layout.
